            </li>

            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-brand-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Multi-language support
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Pillar 3 -->
    <div class="group relative rounded-2xl border border-black/5 bg-white p-8 shadow-soft transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:border-brand-gold/25 hover:shadow-2xl flex flex-col">
      <!-- ✅ Your number (UNCHANGED) -->
      <div class="absolute -top-6 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2">
        <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center rounded-full justify-center bg-white text-lg font-bold text-black shadow-soft">
          03
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ✅ Your image (UNCHANGED) -->
      <div class="-mx-8 -mt-8 h-48 overflow-hidden rounded-t-2xl">
        <img
          src={Image6}
          alt="Deploy the service"
          class="h-full w-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- ✅ Adjusted content BELOW image only -->
      <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-5 pt-6">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-brand-navy">
              <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-brand-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4 4 0 003 15z" />
              </svg>
            </div>

            <div>
              <span class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-navy">Deployment Focus</span>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Seamless Transition</h3>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="text-gray-600 proseish">
            Final briefings, travel coordination, and practical preparation for success.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-auto border-t border-black/5 pt-6">
          <ul class="space-y-3 proseish">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-brand-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Travel arrangement
            </li>

            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <svg class="mt-0.5 h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-brand-gold" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" aria-hidden="true">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
              Onboarding support
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


    <!-- Testimonial Section -->
    <div class="relative mt-32">
      <div class="absolute -left-8 top-1/2 hidden -translate-y-1/2 lg:block">
        <div class="text-6xl font-bold text-gray-200 opacity-50">"</div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-navy/5 to-brand-gold/10 p-8 shadow-soft backdrop-blur-sm md:p-12 lg:p-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-3xl section-title">
              Trusted by global teams for seamless international placements
            </h3>

            <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-gray-700 proseish">
              "The structured approach and dedicated support made our international hiring process smooth and efficient.
              From compliance to deployment, every step was clearly communicated."
            </p>

            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="mr-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-navy font-bold text-brand-gold">
                SJ
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-bold text-gray-900">Sarah Johnson</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600">HR Director, TechGlobal Inc.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 flex items-center space-x-2">
